title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 4 7PM' game
maintext:
PORTLAND, Ore. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Tuesday evening’s drawing of the Oregon Lottery’s “Pick 4 7PM” game were:
5-7-2-6
(five, seven, two, six)
